[Arcane Mastery]
INNATE - ENDLESS MANA: Whenever Ryze hits an enemy with an ability, he gains 2 - 10 (based on level) maximum mana.

INNATE - ARCHMAGE: Whenever Ryze casts an ability, his ability cooldowns are reduced by 1 - 5 (based on level) seconds (reduced by ability haste).

