[Rune Prison]
COST: 20 / 30 / 40 / 50 / 60 MANA
COOLDOWN: 9 / 8 / 7 / 6 / 5
ACTIVE: Ryze seizes the target enemy, dealing magic damage and slowing them for 1 second.

MAGIC DAMAGE:
30 / 45 / 60 / 75 / 90 (+ 15% AP) (+ 1.5% bonus mana)
SLOW:
20 / 25 / 30 / 35 / 40%

FLUX BONUS: Rune Prison spreads to surrounding fluxed enemies.

[Spell Flux]
COST: 50 / 45 / 40 / 35 / 30 MANA
COOLDOWN: 3 / 2.5 / 2 / 1.5 / 1
ACTIVE: Ryze projects an orb upon the target enemy that deals magic damage.

The target and surrounding enemies are also marked with Flux for 3 seconds. Ryze's basic abilities against Flux targets consume the mark to become empowered with an additional effect.

MAGIC DAMAGE:
20 / 30 / 40 / 50 / 60 (+ 15% AP) (+ 0.5% bonus mana)
FLUX BONUS: Spell Flux damages all fluxed enemies spreads farther.

[Desperate Power]
COOLDOWN: 80 / 70 / 60

ACTIVE: For a duration, Ryze gains bonus omnivamp, bonus ability haste, bonus movement speed, the ability to move while casting abilities, and his basic abilities cast a second time dealing reduced damage.

